WEBVTT

00:01.492 --> 00:02.723
Oh, goody, you're all here.

00:02.843 --> 00:05.579
Now, I know I'm not supposed to talk
about my campaign in the office,

00:05.699 --> 00:08.730
but last night I've made a decision
about who should be my campaign manager.

00:08.850 --> 00:10.667
This is a huge job.

00:10.685 --> 00:12.903
This is going to require
a lot of late night,

00:12.938 --> 00:14.855
one-on-one jam sessions
with me,

00:14.890 --> 00:16.373
and we're going to bounce ideas
off of each other,

00:16.408 --> 00:17.524
you're going to have to take
calls for me,

00:17.559 --> 00:19.310
any time, day or night.

00:19.344 --> 00:24.315
The person I have chosen is,
drum roll please,

00:28.420 --> 00:29.787
Ann Perkins! Yay!
Give it up for Ann!

00:29.821 --> 00:32.823
Good choice.

00:32.841 --> 00:34.825
Leslie, I don't know the first
thing about running

00:34.859 --> 00:36.860
a political campaign.

00:36.895 --> 00:38.829
Ann, you beautiful tropical fish.

00:38.847 --> 00:42.049
You're smart as a whip
and you're cool under pressure.

00:42.100 --> 00:44.268
You've resuscitated a human
heart in your bare hands.

00:44.302 --> 00:45.703
No, I haven't.

00:45.737 --> 00:47.271
- You haven't?
- No!

00:47.305 --> 00:49.306
You will.
You're that good of a nurse.

00:49.341 --> 00:50.557
What about Ben?

00:50.609 --> 00:52.526
I mean, he ran for mayor
at 18 and won.

00:52.560 --> 00:54.845
Ben is poison in my campaign.

00:54.863 --> 00:57.514
Our relationship is the reason
why my advisors pulled out.

00:57.549 --> 00:58.899
- I--
- Ann,

00:58.950 --> 01:00.851
don't listen to your head
or your heart.

01:00.885 --> 01:02.686
Just look at my eyes
and say "yes."

01:02.704 --> 01:04.354
- Okay, yes.
- Yes!

01:04.372 --> 01:06.189
- I believe in you, Ann.
- Thank you.

01:06.207 --> 01:07.875
And your first job
as my campaign manager

01:07.909 --> 01:09.660
is to start dressing like one.

01:09.694 --> 01:11.412
I don't want to have this
conversation again.

01:11.463 --> 01:14.197
Again? You just hired me eight
seconds ago.

01:14.215 --> 01:15.833
Wow. You're doing
a really bad job.

